message.content:
A compact kitchen occupies one corner, with black base and wall cabinets forming an L-shape around a light-colored countertop. At the left side of this countertop, below a wooden-framed window, sits a metal sink. Moving right along the counter, a small cooking pot rests on the stovetop beneath a wooden-framed range hood. Toward the far right of the countertop, a cereal box (“Chucky Harps”) stands beside an orange mug and a jar of jam. Nearby, another cereal box (“Rice Bubbles”) is positioned in front of a second “Chucky Harps” box. Farther along the counter, closer to the fridge, are stacked white plates, a box of strawberry-flavored gelatin (“Jello”), a small container of salt (“Alpen Salt”), and another jar of strawberry jam. Above these items are black overhead cabinets; below are matching black lower cabinets. A tall black pantry cabinet stands flush with a white refrigerator on its right, and the refrigerator forms the boundary between the kitchen area and the adjoining dining space.

In the dining area, a rectangular wooden table is surrounded by white upholstered chairs. Centered on the table is a white bowl containing several oranges. Beside the bowl, a large water bottle stands upright in a small holder, and next to it is a rectangular box of snack or cookie mix. An empty wine glass and a clear pitcher sit near the center of the table, and a silvery device (appearing like a laptop) rests to the side of the fruit bowl. A simple white door is set in the wall behind the table, and a round ceiling light fixture hangs overhead. The floor throughout is wood parquet, and the walls are plain white.
